Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:34.14,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胜负仅此一回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:37.24,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}此刻 点燃烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:44.70,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一步步地逼近 我所追求的更多赐予
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:48.68,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在被他人盗走前 你看 爱在燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:50.94,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感触到了热气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:56.12,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火辣辣的 刺激的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:56.12,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1890, 180)\blur3\fs30}去感受它 去感受它 去感受它
